# Part 4A - Installing and Configuring the Jenkins Server

In this section, we will prepare the Jenkins Server for Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment (CI/CD).

At the end of this section, you will have a fully functional Jenkins server with the required tools installed to build Docker images and deploy applications to your Kubernetes cluster.

---

# Jenkins Architecture

```text
                     GitHub Repository
                            │
                            │
                            ▼
                     Jenkins Server
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │      Jenkins        │
                │---------------------│
                │ Git                 │
                │ Docker              │
                │ kubectl             │
                │ Java                │
                │ AWS CLI             │
                └──────────┬──────────┘
                           │
               Builds Docker Image
                           │
                           ▼
                     Docker Hub
                           │
                           ▼
                  Kubernetes Cluster
```

---

# Server Details

| Server | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| jenkins-server | CI/CD Server |

---

