# Part 4C-2B - Automating CI/CD using GitHub Webhooks

In this section, we will automate the complete CI/CD process by integrating GitHub with Jenkins using **GitHub Webhooks**.

Once configured, every code push to GitHub will automatically trigger the Jenkins Pipeline.

By the end of this section, the complete CI/CD workflow will be:

Developer Push Code

↓

GitHub Webhook

↓

Jenkins Pipeline

↓

Build Docker Image

↓

Push Docker Image

↓

Deploy to Kubernetes

↓

Rolling Update

↓

Application Updated

---

