# Common Troubleshooting

## Webhook Not Triggering

Verify

- GitHub Webhook URL
- Jenkins is accessible from GitHub
- Build Trigger is enabled

---

## Docker Push Failed

Verify

```
dockerhub-creds
```

Check Docker Hub permissions.

---

## Deployment Failed

Verify

```bash
kubectl get pods
```

Describe the failing Pod.

```bash
kubectl describe pod <pod-name>
```

---

## ImagePullBackOff

Verify

- Image exists
- Image name matches deployment.yaml
- Repository is public or imagePullSecrets are configured

---

## Rollout Failed

Check

```bash
kubectl rollout status deployment/flask-deployment
```

Describe Pods

```bash
kubectl describe pod <pod-name>
```

