# Completed CI/CD Pipeline

Congratulations!

You have successfully implemented an end-to-end CI/CD pipeline using:

- GitHub
- Jenkins
- Docker
- Docker Hub
- Kubernetes (kubeadm)
- Rolling Updates
- GitHub Webhooks

The pipeline automatically:

1. Detects code changes in GitHub.
2. Builds a Docker image.
3. Tags the image with the Jenkins build number.
4. Pushes the image to Docker Hub.
5. Deploys the application to Kubernetes.
6. Performs a rolling update.
7. Verifies the deployment.
8. Makes the updated application available with minimal downtime.

